# ChangeLog for vserver-utils

  02 Feb 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> src/libvconfig/vconfig.h,
  src/libvconfig/single.c, src/libvconfig/main.c, src/libvconfig/Makefile.am,
  -src/libvconfig/dummy.c:
  libvconfig cleanup

  30 Jan 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> m4/libs.m4, configure.ac,
  src/tools/Makefile.am:
  dietlibc is now mandatory; i.e. no more glibc support!

  30 Jan 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> +src/libinternal,
  src/libvconfig/main.c, src/libvconfig/single.c, src/Makefile.am, configure.ac:
  Local printf functions for dietlibc compatibility

  30 Jan 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> -src/*.c, +src/tools,
  src/Makefile.am, configure.ac:
  Source reorganization

  27 Jan 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> -scripts/commands/enter.sh:
  Remove enter command (use login instead)

  27 Jan 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> src/vexec.c, src/vnamespace.c,
  scripts/lib/vps.sh:
  Add sysvrc init style + cleanup

  26 Jan 2006; Benedikt Böhm <hollow@gentoo.org> m4/libs.m4, configure.ac,
  etc/makefile.am, -etc/examples/context.conf, +etc/fstab, +etc/mtab,
  +etc/procfs.conf, scripts/Makefile.am, scripts/commands/enter.sh,
  scripts/commands/info.sh, scripts/commands/procfs.sh, scripts/commands/stop.sh,
